<br />
This is a basic mains deck, with a solid Kessel drain to depend on most games. The Camp and Civil Disorder(V) are optional starts over Wokling(V), but remember that Mon Mothma(V) is a senator, and Civil Disorder(V) adds to her deploy cost, so therefore I wouldn&#39;t recommend starting that(unless against DS Senate). The Camp is obviously to start against aliens decks. On your opponent&#39;s turn, you pull Reeiken(V) and Mothma(V), then on your first turn deploy them both to Chripa&#39;s Hut to pull Kessel and the Echo War room to remove all 0&#39;s from your deck. This also helps set up your anti-Walkers Mothma(V) right away, so you don&#39;t have to dig for her in decks you don&#39;t start Strike Planning. From there, set up at Kessel with your big ships, and attack the opponent continuously with your characters. <br />
<br />
Some interesting notes: <br />
Chewbacca (V) pulls Life Debt for you. <br />
Reeiken (V) pulls Captain Han Solo, so reveal the Falcon to pull Chewbacca(V) if possible and then use Reeiken to get out the Captain. <br />
Hear Me Baby, Hold Together is MONSTER anti-cannon tech, as it works to protect even your capitals! <br />
Artoo, Brave Little Droid protects you from Lateral Damage, and can cancel a battle destiny in battle. Use Threepio With Parts Showing to pull him back into hand every turn to redeploy! <br />
<br />
